{"tid":2070442,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"其實連登仔知唔知點解LastofUs2咁高評分？","createTime":"2020-06-19T06:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T04:33:15.000Z","uid":323922,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f1501a39092028779a6043cba9bc2ed29ab5d80c","tid":2070442,"uid":323922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:38:15.000Z","msg":"之前睇左個post，啲人話LoU2好高分會好玩。我住喺美國，比較明白呢度既文化。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLast of Us 2高調玩女權、跨性別LGBTQ，你估下如果評分雜誌比低分會比所有左翼人士屌到點？而且大部份遊戲雜誌出左名親左，係人都知道啲評分係假，為左討好大聲左膠一定迫住比滿分。<br />\n<br />\n所以大家睇定啲先，唔好信評分，得閒建議大家睇多啲外國遊戲Youtubers，例如TheQuartering或者GeeksAndGamers <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e31a2aa87618ff4e051ba6f299176e7a327a4b","tid":2070442,"uid":78039,"like":3,"dislike":45,"score":-42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:39:09.000Z","msg":"睇達哥今晚玩就知正唔正"},{"pid":"6d615eeb5693137e988b4ae5bf25f313a2c1eb5f","tid":2070442,"uid":211046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:42:41.000Z","msg":"啲左膠重惡撚過共產黨，香港至少未有國民教育，美國（至少加州）大撚把左膠教育，滲撚哂入你大學major到。"},{"pid":"7717f0374f2b2257bf90a6f208e605a296268e96","tid":2070442,"uid":323922,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:45:54.000Z","msg":"大家千祈唔好買，如果唔係LoU2賺得，我保證將來隻隻game啲劇情都係咁，所有角色都係變性人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5c23bb9555d95628560036895482acb1da8986","tid":2070442,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7717f0374f2b2257bf90a6f208e605a296268e96","tid":2070442,"uid":323922,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:45:54.000Z","msg":"大家千祈唔好買，如果唔係LoU2賺得，我保證將來隻隻game啲劇情都係咁，所有角色都係變性人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T06:49:05.